🌟 Fun Number Guessing Game
A vibrant, kid-friendly web application where players guess a secret magic number between 1 and 100. This project features bouncy animations, colorful feedback, and interactive elements designed to make learning logic fun!

🚀 Features
Kids-First Design: Bright colors, large fonts, and emoji-based feedback.

Interactive Animations: Uses Animate.css and custom CSS transforms for a "3D" feel.

Smart Logic: Real-time feedback (Too High / Too Low) to guide the player.

Keyboard Friendly: Press the Enter key to submit guesses instantly.

Win State: Celebratory animations and a "Play Again" button when the number is found.

🛠️ Built With
HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript (Vanilla)

Animate.css: For professional-grade entrance and feedback animations.

📁 File Structure
index.html: The main entry point containing the game structure.

style.css: All the visual styling and kid-friendly themes.

script.js: The game mechanics and input handling.

🕹️ How to Play
Open index.html in any web browser.

Enter a number between 1 and 100 in the box.

Click the "Guess!" button or press Enter.

Follow the emoji hints (📈 for higher, 📉 for lower).

Find the magic number to see the trophy! 🏆